ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 181 (Alberta)
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 181 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of ALBERTA, with respect to the SEVERE FLOODING, that affected the province, from June 16 to June 24, 2014.
